---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="Learn about this blog and the person behind it."
>
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif font-bold text-surface-900 dark:text-white mb-8">
      About
    </h1>

    <div class="prose text-surface-700 dark:text-surface-300">
      <p>
        Welcome to <strong>Haseeb Studio Blogs</strong> — a tech-focused blog where I share practical knowledge,
        tutorials, and insights from real-world development experience.
      </p>

      <p>
        I'm <strong>Haseeb Ahmad</strong>, a full-stack developer with 7+ years of experience building
        scalable web applications using modern technologies like Python, JavaScript/TypeScript,
        React, Vue, and cloud platforms.
      </p>

      <h2>The Tech Stack</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Astro</strong> — A fast, modern static site generator built for content</li>
        <li><strong>Tailwind CSS</strong> — Utility-first CSS for clean, responsive design</li>
        <li><strong>Vercel</strong> — Hosting and automatic deployments</li>
        <li><strong>n8n</strong> — Open-source workflow automation</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Purpose</h2>
      <p>
        This blog is created to help developers, students, and tech enthusiasts learn faster and build better.
        Here you'll find:
      </p>

      <ul>
        <li>Step-by-step coding tutorials</li>
        <li>Backend & frontend development guides</li>
        <li>Cloud & deployment strategies</li>
        <li>Real-world problem-solving approaches</li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        Whether you're just starting out or already experienced, the goal is to provide clear,
        actionable, and practical content.
      </p>

      <p>
        If you’d like to connect or collaborate, feel free to reach out via the contact page.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
